item.title: [718] Tree top respawning?
item.dc:creator: @MoreWeed MoreWeed
item.description:
@MoreWeed wrote:

I’ve removed both parts of a tree:

				//bottom half
				World.deleteObject(new WorldTile(3097, 3502, 0));
				//top half
				World.deleteObject(new WorldTile(3096, 3501, 1));

However after some time, the top half reappears, any ideas what’s causing this to happen? and how can I stop this from happening?

Any help would be much appreciated.
